<!--                                               -->
<!-- A sample xml input file for CMakeCreator.py   --> 
<!--                                               -->
<!-- Typical usage consists of copying and         -->
<!-- editing. Edits are often deletions of         -->
<!-- unnecessary optional parameters.              -->
